# Dogfood: mnema runs against itself in this repo, so this .mnema/ is a
# development workbench, not a reference project — ignored WHOLESALE.
#
# This is a deliberate exception for the tool's OWN repo. Adopter projects do
# the opposite (and `mnema init` scaffolds a .gitignore that commits the chain
# and public keys, ignoring only the rebuildable state/cache and the private
# key). The faithful examples of the audit flow are those adopter repos, never
# this one.
.mnema/
